data.description: This is the total package! Beautifully maintained home on an incredible lot that backs to private wooded land and just steps away to neighborhood park. Enjoy a spacious floorplan with many updates! Inviting and large foyer with flared staircase leads to a vaulted upper level living room with new LVP flooring (2023).  Kitchen features newer stainless steel appliances and a walk-in corner pantry that opens to dining area with sliders to a large deck (2020).  Generous sized primary bedroom with walk-in closet and w/t full bathroom - 3 bedrooms on this level! You'll love the walkout lower level - flared stairs w/ new carpet lead to a spacious family room featuring an attractive gas fireplace.  4th bedroom, 3/4 bath, & more storage completes this area.  Newer driveway (2022), newer roof (2022), storage shed, playground set. REGARDING SCHOOLS: Farmington, Hastings & Randolph all have busing available in this neighborhood!
